docs {
  Get a conversation with all its turns. Returns full conversation details
  including each turn's query, response, sources, reasoning steps, and metadata.

  Replace :session_id with the actual session ID from a previous streaming request.

  ## Turn Fields

  Each turn in the conversation includes:

  | Field | Type | Description |
  |-------|------|-------------|
  | turn_number | int | Sequential turn number |
  | query | string | The user's question |
  | response | string | The agent's full response |
  | sources | array | Retrieved chunks used to generate the response |
  | thinking_steps | array | Agent reasoning steps (guardrail, retrieval, grading, generation) |
  | citations | array | Paper citations referenced in the response |
  | pending_confirmation | object or null | Active HITL confirmation awaiting user decision |
  | execution_time_ms | int | Time taken for this turn |
  | provider | string | LLM provider used |
  | model | string | Model used |
  | created_at | string | ISO 8601 timestamp |

  ## Authentication

  Requires authentication. Returns 404 if conversation not found or not owned by user.
}
